Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,金鱼死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怜
